    "body": "Since the total perimeter is $` 20 \\text{ m}, `\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\" columnalign=\"right left\"><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mi>b</mi></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{align*} 3a + 2b &= 20\n\t\\\\ 2b &= 20 - 3a\n\t\\\\ b &= \\frac{20 - 3a}{2}\n\\end{align*}\n```\n\n\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\" columnalign=\"right left\"><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mi>A</mi></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mspace width=\"0.1667em\"></mspace></mrow><msup><mn>60</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>20</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mi>a</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{align*} A &= ab + \\frac{1}{2}a^2\\sin 60^\\circ\n\t\\\\  &= ab + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}a^2}{4}\n\t\\\\  &= a\\left( \\frac{20 - 3a}{2} \\right) + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}a^2}{4}\n\t\\\\  &= \\frac{20a - 3a^2}{2} + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}a^2}{4}\n\t\\\\ \\frac{{\\rm d}A}{{\\rm d}a} &= 10 - 3a + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}a}{2}\n\\end{align*}\n```\n\n\nAt maximum $`A,`\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\"><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mn>10</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mi>a</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mfrac><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mi>a</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo form=\"prefix\" stretchy=\"false\">−</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo form=\"prefix\" stretchy=\"false\">−</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4.6861</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{gather*} \\frac{{\\rm d}A}{{\\rm d}a} = 0\n\t\\\\ 10 - 3a + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}a}{2} = 0\n\t\\\\ \\frac{\\sqrt{3}a}{2} - 3a = - 10\n\t\\\\ a\\left( \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} - 3 \\right) = - 10\n\t\\\\ a = 4.6861\n\\end{gather*}\n```\n\n\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\" columnalign=\"right left\"><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mi>A</mi></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>20</mn><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><mn>4.6861</mn><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><msup><mn>4.6861</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"prefix\">(</mo><msup><mn>4.6861</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo fence=\"true\" form=\"postfix\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>23.43</mn><msup><mtext> m</mtext><mn>2</mn></msup><mtext>(4 s.f.)</mtext><mspace width=\"0.2778em\"></mspace><mi>∎</mi></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{align*} A &= \\frac{20\\left( 4.6861 \\right) - 3\\left( 4.6861^2 \\right)}{2} + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}\\left( 4.6861^2 \\right)}{4}\n\t\\\\ &= 23.43 \\text{ m}^2 \\text{(4 s.f.)} \\; \\QED\n\\end{align*}\n```\n\n\n\n``` =html\n<div class=\"display-math-container\">\n<math display=\"block\" class=\"tml-display\" style=\"display:block math;\"><mtable displaystyle=\"true\" columnalign=\"right left\"><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mo form=\"prefix\" stretchy=\"false\">−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>=</mo><mo form=\"prefix\" stretchy=\"false\">−</mo><mn>2.1340</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd class=\"tml-right\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd class=\"tml-left\" style=\"padding:0.7ex 0em 0.7ex 0em;\"><mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math>\n</div>\n```\n\n``` =tex\n\\begin{align*} \\frac{{\\rm d}^2A}{{\\rm d}a^2} &= - 3 + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\n\t\\\\  &= -2.1340 \\\\ &< 0\n\\end{align*}\n```\n\n\nHence $` {A= 23.43} `\nis a maximum $` \\QED  `\n"
